{"word":"G1894 - ἐπειδή - epeidḗ - ep-i-day' - After that","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπειδή</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epeidḗ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-i-day'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">After that</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Conjunction / இணைப்புச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"படியினால், ஆதலால் - இடைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"when now, since now"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1893 - ἐπεί - epeí - ep-i'/1893\">G1893</a> and <a href=\"#/G1211 - δή - dḗ - day/1211\">G1211</a>; <i>since now</i>, that is, (of time) <i>when</i>, or (of cause) <i>whereas:</i> - after that, because, for, (that, -asmuch as), seeing, since.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}